data.description: Welcome to charming downtown Nicholasville and this beautiful remodeled historic home built in 1871. The perfect fusion of historic charm and modern amenities, it offers gorgeous refinished hardwood floors amidst numerous contemporary updates. Fully updated kitchen with plenty of cabinetry and granite countertops, large island and stainless steel appliances.  Loaded with charm, there are two fireplaces and crown molding and beautiful trim throughout.  The primary ensuite is the perfect place to relax and unwind.  Double vanity and a beautiful clawfoot tub and walk-in shower.  3 additional bedrooms and 1 more full bath.  Half bath on the first floor.  3rd floor features a large flex room with direct access to the back yard through the spiral staircase.  Would make a great play room or media room.  Outside you will find a wrap around porch to enjoy all the sights of downtown living, loaded with southern charm. Schedule your showing today!
